data.description: - 187 GRIZZLY RD ROYAL, AR 71968 This beautifully remodeled two-story home nestled perfectly between Lake Ouachita and Lake Hamilton sits on just over 9.5 acres with a catfish pond, pasture-lined creek, tongue-and-groove pine, and two large decks for those warm summer nights watching fireflies dance.   Remodeled in 2018 with granite countertops, hickory cabinets, and new stainless steel appliances, the gorgeously updated kitchen is ready for entertaining alongside the living room’s high ceilings and brick fireplace.   Spacious but private double-masters provide their own retreat from the main floor complete with dual on-suites and walk-in closets. The larger master includes ground to ceiling windows, a custom designed double vanity, large, tiled shower, personal A/C, and private deck doors. An outdoor-lover's dream with RV parking and plug-ins, an open on-site barn, and an insulated 30x40’ shop with 12’ walls and 110/220 power. There’s no toy, task, or tool this home can’t house.  A/C replaced in 2018, water-heater replaced in 2019, this home rests on a slab foundation with updated city plumbing (both coming and going). The property is zoned for both agriculture and livestock.
